<div class="content" name="CLUSCTL_RESOURCE_NETNAME_CHECK_OU_PERMISSIONS_OUTPUT" uuid="8d7636aa-9016-4e25-a769-b000aed84012"><p>The <b>CLUSCTL_RESOURCE_NETNAME_CHECK_OU_PERMISSIONS_OUTPUT</b>
